Subject: [Caml-list] Gg 0.9.0

Hello, 

I'd like to announce the release of Gg 0.9.0 which should be available shortly in opam. 

There are a few renamings regarding matrices; sorry about the inconvenience but the current scheme was a little bit confusing and inconvenient when one decided to switch code to a matrix of higher dimensionality. There are also other changes and additions, get all the details in the release notes:

  https://github.com/dbuenzli/gg/blob/v0.9.0/CHANGES.md

Gg is an OCaml module providing basic types for computer graphics and geometry.

Home page: http://erratique.ch/software/gg

Best,

Daniel
